commit.message: Fix link-local scan results error message
Add missing options
Add missing options
Replace internet-draft names with RFC numbers
Add support to measure changes of the Flow Label value
Add port number randomization. Make port number randomization and source address randomization dependent on --flood-sources and --flood-ports. Fix verbose printouts.
If the Ack Number has not been explicitly set, then set it to 0 if the ACK bit is not set, or otherwise randomize it.
Increase the maximum number of allowed EHs
Fix printout of source prefix
Always copy IFACE_LENGTH bytes. The change is not really necessary since we always set [IFACE_LENGTH-1] to 0. But the change keeps the code consistent
Always compare and copy IFACE_LENGTH bytes
